cs.RO, cs.SD, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper presents a novel approach for interactive auditory object analysis with a humanoid robot. 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper focuses on gathering audio signals from microphones embedded in the robotic ears and analyzing properties of the contents of the containers. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper presents a system for interactive auditory exploration with a humanoid robot. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses a neural network architecture to learn from the gathered audio signals and analyze properties of the contents of the containers. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses a deep neural network architecture to analyze properties of the contents of the containers.
